          "childMarkdownRemark": {
            "html": "<h1 id=\"simple-blog---gatsby-theme\"><a href=\"#simple-blog---gatsby-theme\" aria-label=\"simple blog   gatsby theme permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Simple blog - Gatsby Theme</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Ready to be used blogging theme</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"-features\"><a href=\"#-features\" aria-label=\" features permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>✨ Features</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Theme UI for styling</li>\n<li>PrismJS highlighting</li>\n<li>Gatsby Image</li>\n<li>Posts in MDX</li>\n<li>Tags</li>\n<li>Static pages for non post types</li>\n<li>SEO friendly</li>\n<li>Fully customizable through <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-plugin-theme-ui</code> and <strong>shadow components</strong></li>\n<li>Linting with ESLint and Stylelint</li>\n<li>Code formatting with Prettier</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"-installation\"><a href=\"#-installation\" aria-label=\" installation permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>🚀 Installation</h2>\n<p>To use this theme in your Gatsby sites, follow these instructions:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Install the theme</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\"># npm\nnpm install --save gatsby-theme-simple-blog\n# yarn\nyarn add gatsby-theme-simple-blog</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Add the theme to your <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-config.js</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">module<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\tplugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"gatsby-theme-simple-blog\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Start your site</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">gatsby develop</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"-configuration\"><a href=\"#-configuration\" aria-label=\" configuration permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>⚙ Configuration</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">module<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\tplugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\tresolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"gatsby-theme-simple-blog\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t\toptions<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\t\tbasePath<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// base url \"/\"</span>\n\t\t\t\ttagsPath<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// tags url \"/tags\"</span>\n\t\t\t\tcontentPath<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// content url for posts\"/content/posts\"</span>\n\t\t\t\tassetPath<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//  assets url \"/content/assets\"</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\tsiteMetadata<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\turl<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"https://abdessalam.dev\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\ttitle<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Simple blog\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\tauthor<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Abdessalam\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\tdescription<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Simple blog theme starter\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\tlocale<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"en\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\tsocialLinks<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">// links displayed in footer</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\t\ttext<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Twitter\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t\t\tlink<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"https://twitter.com/gatsbyjs\"</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\t\ttext<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"GitHub\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t\t\tlink<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"https://github.com/gatsbyjs\"</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\tnavLinks<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">// links display in navbar</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\t\ttext<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Home\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t\t\tlink<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"/\"</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\t\ttext<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"About\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t\t\tlink<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"/about\"</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\t\ttext<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Contact\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\t\t\tlink<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"/contact\"</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n\t\tthemeConfig<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t\tthemeSwitcher<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// enable theme switcher</span>\n\t\t\tshowNavLinks<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// show links from navLinks array in navbar</span>\n\t\t\tloadMorePosts<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// enable load more posts</span>\n\t\t\tpostsPerPage<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// posts to display per page</span>\n\t\t\tpostsIncrementBy<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// posts increment value</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"-customization\"><a href=\"#-customization\" aria-label=\" customization permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>💅 Customization</h2>\n<p>You can override theme components using <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/blog/2019-04-29-component-shadowing/\">Component Shadowing</a></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Create a folder with theme name <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-theme-simple-blog</code></li>\n<li>Override any component you want by creating a new one and its css file, for example <code class=\"language-text\">Nav.js</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">Nav.css</code></li>\n<li>You can also override <a href=\"https://theme-ui.com/getting-started\">theme-ui</a> theme style by creating <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-plugin-theme-ui</code> folder and new object style or components</li>\n<li>You can also override or add new global css styles in assets as they are imported in <code class=\"language-text\">globalStyle.js</code></li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"-writing-content\"><a href=\"#-writing-content\" aria-label=\" writing content permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>✍ Writing content</h2>\n<p>Example of release post in <code class=\"language-text\">content/posts/[POST_TITLE]/index.mdx</code></p>\n<p>You can create pages by passing type to <code class=\"language-text\">page</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">---\ntype: post\ntitle: Another post\ndate: 2019-07-23\ndraft: false\nmedia: ./img1.jpeg\nauthor: Abdessalam\ntags:\n  - Hello\n  - Post\n  - Welcome\n---\n\nContent goes here</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"🧐-whats-inside\"><a href=\"#%F0%9F%A7%90-whats-inside\" aria-label=\"🧐 whats inside permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>🧐 What’s inside?</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">.\n├── node_modules\n├── src\n|   ├── assets\n|   ├── components\n|   |   ├── Layout.js\n|